rnal Link"class="fa-external-link-square-alt fas"title="External Link"> </span>borderlands.com</a>.</div><div class="step 2">If you have not already registered and signed in to <strong>SHiFT</strong>, you will be prompted to do so.</div><div class="step 3">Select <em>SHiFT</em> from the menu, then choose <em>Redeem Code</em>.</div><div class="step 4">Once you have reached the <strong>Code Redemption</strong> page, select <em>SHiFT Codes</em> from the list of options.</div><div class="step 5">Enter the 25-character SHiFT Code into the provided field. Once you are finished, click <em>Check</em>.</div><div class="step 6">If the SHiFT Code is available for multiple platforms, you will be prompted to select which platform the SHiFT Code should be redeemed for. You can redeem the SHiFT Code for as many platforms as you would like.</div><div class="step 7">If successful, you will receive a confirmation message. If the SHiFT Code is for <em>Borderlands: The Pre-Sequel</em> or <em>Borderlands 3</em>, additional steps are required to receive your rewards. Refer to the <a aria-label="How to Redeem SHiFT Codes in Borderlands: The Pre-Sequel"class=themed href=tps#step_8 title="How to Redeem SHiFT Codes in Borderlands: The Pre-Sequel">Borderlands: The Pre-Sequel</a> and <a aria-label="How to Redeem SHiFT Codes in Borderlands 3"class=themed href=bl3#step_6 title="How to Redeem SHiFT Codes in Borderlands 3">Borderlands 3</a> instructions respectively for more information.</div></div><?php include_once('local/support-footer.php'); ?><?php include_once('global/afterContent.php'); ?><?php include_once('global/sharedScripts.php'); ?><script async src="/assets/scripts/min/local/help/how-to-redeem/instructions.min.js?v=<?php echo $svQueryString; ?>"></script>